Add file /etc/apt/sources.list.d/dmx-repo.list
 * deb https://download.dmx.systems/repos/ubuntu/ xenial/

Add key:
 * curl -fsSL https://download.dmx.systems/repos/gpg | sudo apt-key add -
 
Install dmx:
 * sudo apt update && sudo apt install dmx
 * edit /etc/dmx/config.properties and change the initial admin password
 * run sudo systemctl start dmx

Known Issues:
 * DMX is still in beta stage and clearly needs further improvement.
    
Feedback:
 * Join https://forum.dmx.systems to help us improve.

Juergen Neumann


